dcterms:description: OpenAI Gym is a toolkit for developing and comparing reinforcement learning algorithms, providing a variety of environments to test and benchmark RL agents.
dcterms:title: OpenAI Gym

dcterms:description: Synthetic Tree is a simple environment defined by a binary decision tree of depth 20, where rewards on edges are sampled uniformly.
dcterms:title: Synthetic Tree

dcterms:description: Algorithmic Tasks include a set of tasks such as Copy, DuplicatedInput, RepeatCopy, Reverse, ReversedAddition, and ReversedAddition3, where agents operate on sequences of characters or digits.
dcterms:title: Algorithmic Tasks
